-- Anheuser-Busch InBev says cutting about 1,400 jobs
-- 
-- Mon Dec 8, 2008 1:40pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/08/businesspro-us-brief-anheuser-busch-inbe-idUSTRE4B75RR20081208

 

 (Reuters) - Anheuser-Busch InBev NV INTB.BR said on Monday the company was cutting about 1,400 U.S. jobs in beer-related divisions. 

 Highlights: * Says about 75 percent of affected jobs are based in St. Louis, downtown offices or at sunset hills campus * Says more than 250 U.S. positions that are currently open will not be filled * Says additional 415 contractor positions will be eliminated * Says most of the reductions will occur by the end of this year * Sees aggregate pre-tax expense associated with the reduction approx $197 million